ActPilotage Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Atlantic Pilotage Tariff Regulations, 1996
PrecisRegulations Amending the ATLANTIC PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS, 1996, to increase pilotage charges in certain compulsory and non-compulsory areas in order to maintain the ability of the Authority to meet its mandate to operate, to help ensure the long-term financial self-sustainability of the Authority as a whole, and to be mindful of the economic fragility of the region.
